title: Dj.Nece's International DJ Mix 13
description:
Thanks for listening in to my mixes I am sure glad 
that I can place this upload just for you.Shout outs
to New York and all you listeners.Here is the playlist:

1.Josh Winiberg-First Light(Electronica Mix)Mixed with Marco Carola-Jackpot(Original Mix)
2.Presure Drop-You Are Mine(Steven Hinz Mix Vs Kabale Und Leibe Remix)Dj.Nece's Prolong Version
3.Aniki-Equilibrium(Original Mix)
4.Atmotion VS Summer Channel-The Undertow Way
(Atmotion's Progressive Mash Up Mix)Great Job Atmotion!
5.Kiko-Steepo
6.Delirium Feat. Sarah Mc Lachlan-Silence(Neils Van Gogh 
VS Thomas Gold Instrumental Dub mixed with Thomas Gold Mix)
7.Ricardo-Change The Scene(Original Mix)
8.Marco Carola-Mini Monkey
9.Ok Corral-Planetarium
10.Simon Blann-Halloween
11.Ultra Nate-Automatic(Tikaro, J Louis and Ferran Remix)
13.Sebastien Leger-Jaguar
No disrespect to the Muslim Community on this mix
14.Mario Piu & Mauro Picotto-Arabian Pleasures(Vocal Remix)
15.Aniki-Evil Nugget(Original Mix)
16.Mc Flipside and Joey Seminara-Just The Tip(Hatiras Vocal Mix)
17.Paul Woolford-Black Orchid(Dub Vs Original Mix)Dj.Nece's Prolong Version
18.Atmotion VS Ann Lee-2 Times After Dark(Atmotion's Dark Room Mash Up Mix)
19.Raudive-A1 Untitled (Number 024)
20.Namito Feat. Mahan-Upload(Butch Remix)
21.Marco Carola-Cortotionist
22.Kiko-One Fifteen(Original Mix)
23.Unkle-Hold My Hand(Evil Nine Remix)

As you read the playlist you find artist that are not well known
these are great artist that the industry just dont have them signed.
As for I listen to the underground stuff from up and coming artist like
Ricardo, Atmotion, Simon Blann and Josh Winiberg they do great work and
just dont get that needed airplay well no more here I am to introduce you
to them with pride!You know the deal spread the word and give feedback about
my mixes this one is long but well deserved rock on for 2009. I hope this year
that I will be your first choice to download.If you have hi5, facebook, or myspace
